<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Sketchbook Mixed Medium on RaihnForge</title><link>https://RaihnForge.github.io/tags/sketchbook-mixed-medium/</link><description>Recent content in Sketchbook Mixed Medium on RaihnForge</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2013 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://RaihnForge.github.io/tags/sketchbook-mixed-medium/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Envelope Art–Step Up</title><link>https://RaihnForge.github.io/art/illustration/envelope-artstep-up/</link><pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2013 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://RaihnForge.github.io/art/illustration/envelope-artstep-up/</guid><description>&lt;p>&lt;a href="http://www.joshuakeyes.us/wordpress/raihn/images/cec0c1640bfc_1033D/fb_envelop_art_07.jpg">&lt;img src="https://RaihnForge.github.io/images/recovered/fb_envelop_art_07_thumb.jpg" alt="fb_envelop_art_07" title="fb_envelop_art_07">&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Its was a while ago that I illustrated this on an envelope and sent it out to my wife while she was away for a on a challenging trip.  I ran across it and thought it might be fun to share.  I’m currently in a life transition, moving across country. This image reminds me that no matter where I step next in life, I better make it a point to step up to the challenge, and ROFL STOMP THAT SHIZZZ!&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Envelope Art</title><link>https://RaihnForge.github.io/art/illustration/envelope-art/</link><pubDate>Thu, 04 Aug 2011 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://RaihnForge.github.io/art/illustration/envelope-art/</guid><description>&lt;p>While my wife was at BMT I attempted to write her every day.  I included an image to hopefully inspire a little joy in the challenging times.  Here are a few of them:&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;a href="https://RaihnForge.github.io/images/recovered/fb_envelop_art_01.jpg">&lt;img src="https://RaihnForge.github.io/images/recovered/fb_envelop_art_01.jpg" alt="fb_envelop_art_01" title="fb_envelop_art_01">&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;a href="https://RaihnForge.github.io/images/recovered/fb_envelop_art_02.jpg">&lt;img src="https://RaihnForge.github.io/images/recovered/fb_envelop_art_02.jpg" alt="fb_envelop_art_02" title="fb_envelop_art_02">&lt;/a>&lt;a href="https://RaihnForge.github.io/images/recovered/fb_envelop_art_03.jpg">&lt;img src="https://RaihnForge.github.io/images/recovered/fb_envelop_art_03.jpg" alt="fb_envelop_art_03" title="fb_envelop_art_03">&lt;/a>&lt;a href="https://RaihnForge.github.io/images/recovered/fb_envelop_art_04.jpg">&lt;img src="https://RaihnForge.github.io/images/recovered/fb_envelop_art_04.jpg" alt="fb_envelop_art_04" title="fb_envelop_art_04">&lt;/a>&lt;a href="https://RaihnForge.github.io/images/recovered/fb_envelop_art_05.jpg">&lt;img src="https://RaihnForge.github.io/images/recovered/fb_envelop_art_05.jpg" alt="fb_envelop_art_05" title="fb_envelop_art_05">&lt;/a>&lt;a href="https://RaihnForge.github.io/images/recovered/fb_envelop_art_06.jpg">&lt;img src="https://RaihnForge.github.io/images/recovered/fb_envelop_art_06.jpg" alt="fb_envelop_art_06" title="fb_envelop_art_06">&lt;/a>&lt;a href="http://www.joshuakeyes.us/wordpress/raihn/images/Envelope-Art_889C/fb_envelop_art_07.jpg">&lt;img src="https://RaihnForge.github.io/images/recovered/fb_envelop_art_07_thumb.jpg" alt="fb_envelop_art_07" title="fb_envelop_art_07">&lt;/a>&lt;a href="http://www.joshuakeyes.us/wordpress/raihn/images/Envelope-Art_889C/fb_envelop_art_08.jpg">&lt;img src="http://www.joshuakeyes.us/wordpress/raihn/images/Envelope-Art_889C/fb_envelop_art_08_thumb.jpg" alt="fb_envelop_art_08" title="fb_envelop_art_08">&lt;/a>&lt;a href="http://www.joshuakeyes.us/wordpress/raihn/images/Envelope-Art_889C/fb_envelop_art_09.jpg">&lt;img src="http://www.joshuakeyes.us/wordpress/raihn/images/Envelope-Art_889C/fb_envelop_art_09_thumb.jpg" alt="fb_envelop_art_09" title="fb_envelop_art_09">&lt;/a>&lt;a href="http://www.joshuakeyes.us/wordpress/raihn/images/Envelope-Art_889C/fb_envelop_art_10.jpg">&lt;img src="http://www.joshuakeyes.us/wordpress/raihn/images/Envelope-Art_889C/fb_envelop_art_10_thumb.jpg" alt="fb_envelop_art_10" title="fb_envelop_art_10">&lt;/a>&lt;a href="http://www.joshuakeyes.us/wordpress/raihn/images/Envelope-Art_889C/fb_envelop_art_11.jpg">&lt;img src="http://www.joshuakeyes.us/wordpress/raihn/images/Envelope-Art_889C/fb_envelop_art_11_thumb.jpg" alt="fb_envelop_art_11" title="fb_envelop_art_11">&lt;/a>&lt;a href="http://www.joshuakeyes.us/wordpress/raihn/images/Envelope-Art_889C/fb_envelop_art_12.jpg">&lt;img src="http://www.joshuakeyes.us/wordpress/raihn/images/Envelope-Art_889C/fb_envelop_art_12_thumb.jpg" alt="fb_envelop_art_12" title="fb_envelop_art_12">&lt;/a>&lt;a href="http://www.joshuakeyes.us/wordpress/raihn/images/Envelope-Art_889C/fb_envelop_art_13.jpg">&lt;img src="http://www.joshuakeyes.us/wordpress/raihn/images/Envelope-Art_889C/fb_envelop_art_13_thumb.jpg" alt="fb_envelop_art_13" title="fb_envelop_art_13">&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>I hope she had as much fun reading them as I did making them &lt;img src="http://www.joshuakeyes.us/wordpress/raihn/images/Envelope-Art_889C/wlEmoticon-openmouthedsmile.png" alt="Open-mouthed smile">&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Keyes Salvage Concept</title><link>https://RaihnForge.github.io/art/illustration/keyes-salvage-concept/</link><pubDate>Tue, 29 Jul 2008 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://RaihnForge.github.io/art/illustration/keyes-salvage-concept/</guid><description>&lt;p>I am working with a 3d model maker/animator who is a good friend of mine. I am contributing concept artwork, designs, and illustrations that will be used to create the 3d characters to be animated into his demo reel.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>-Page under heavy construction-&lt;/p>
