&lt;p>Good Times at the Track&lt;/p>
&lt;p>This is a sketch that I later colored with photoshop while I was visiting my dad in the pits of Reno-Fernley Raceway. We hung out most of the weekend dispensing fuel to the drivers. We played some cards, chatted, and watched the races. Memories to treasure, indeed.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="http://www.joshuakeyes.us/raihn/images/reno-raceway_sketch.jpg" alt="">&lt;/p>
